data.description: Newly remodeled all on walk-in level gorgeous maple hardwood floors master and bath, guest and bath, kitchen and dining, plus guest room upstairs and downstairs. This custom home was built and owned by a local contractor using best quality. in a fishing community in coveted Timberline Estates. 2 min to Scenic Lake Taneycomo overview. 8 min to public boat launch on Bull Shoals Lake and Swan Creek access. Tucked into quaint small town of Forsyth but 20 min from historic Branson Entertainment and Table Rock Lake.
